<div class="content">
	<div class="container-fluid"><h1>Membership</h1>
<p>Torrey Pines Gulls Radio Control Soaring Society, Inc. (TPG) is a not-for-profit corporation whose purpose is to support and encourage member participation in the hobby/sport of model sailplane flying. TPG is an AMA chartered club and therefore proof of membership in the Academy of Model Aeronautics (AMA) is a prerequisite for TPG membership. Membership in AMA provides liability and property damage insurance while operating model aircraft safely and with the permission of the site owner.</p>
<p>Note: You are required by the Gliderport operator, Air California Adventure, LLC, to annually sign a liability waiver form at the Gliderport office/shop before permission to fly at Torrey Pines Gliderport will be granted.</p>
<p>The form below may be used to apply for, or renew membership in TPG. Dues are as follows:</p>
<p>Full Members – $60 per year<br />
Junior rate up to 19 is $5<br />
Student rate 19 or older is  $30 per year<br />
Receive a credit of up to $20 on your membership dues. $10.00 per each half-day working at any TPG  flying field<br />
New members joining in the first six months of the year pay the full rate.  Those joining in July through September pay half the applicable rate.  If you are a new member joining in October through December you pay the full rate but your membership is considered paid through the end of the following year.</p>
<p>Please pay online using PayPal, which allows payment using PayPal, debit or credit card. If however, you choose to pay by check or cash, please email the membership chairman at: membership@torreypinesgulls.org to receive a membership application form. When the form is completed, please mail your membership application and payment using the provided pre-addressed return envelope.</p>
<p>The results of the form will be electronically submitted to TPG’s membership chairman. You will also receive an email of the form results as a confirmation. Please be sure to provide your email address on the application.</p>
<p>AMA membership is required and you can verify your membership here: AMA Verification.</p>
<p>AMA Membership application is at: AMA Application.</p>
<p>Please submit form information before completing PayPal payment information.  </p>	</div>
</div>

